nosd (0.1.1-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Harden service: keep ProtectSystem=strict and NoNewPrivileges=true.
  * Allow writes via ReadWritePaths=/etc/nos /var/lib/nos /run.
  * Use StateDirectory=nos and ConfigurationDirectory=nos.
  * Add sysusers/tmpfiles for nosd user/group and dirs.

